result.execSummary:
The defendant Rose Marie Kuehni was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. On one or more other charges, Rose Marie Kuehni was found not guilty. These charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Rose Marie Kuehni is presumed innocent of the not guilty charges.

  • Rose Marie Kuehni was found guilty of Hiding a Corpse, a class G felony, Wisconsin Statutes 940.11(2).
  • Rose Marie Kuehni was found guilty of Aggravated Battery-Intend GreatBod. Harm, a class E felony, Wisconsin Statutes 940.19(5).
